[[Image:Location-Europe-UNsubregions, Kosovo as part of Serbia.png|thumb|240px|right|Map of Europe coded by region according to the [[United Nations geoscheme for Europe]].]] This is a '''list of [[herbaria]] in Europe''', organized first by region where the herbarium is located (using the [[United Nations geoscheme for Europe]]), then within each region by size of the collection. For other continents, see [[List of herbaria]].
